          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-indigo-100 border-l-[4px] border-[#4F46E5] p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-indigo-900 font-medium">
            <strong>THE BRUTAL TRUTH:</strong> Investors judge your product by your website. Generic template = "we're like everyone else." Custom design = "we're different, we care, we're capable." Your website is your first product demo. Make it count.
